  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Marketing Intern",
  "description": "<h3><strong>About Us</strong></h3>\n<p>Trisafe Biotech Pte Ltd. is a biotech startup, spin off from A*STAR. We are an antimicrobial solution provider where we work to develop state-of-the-art polyionene-infused skincare products that are safe, effective and suitable for extended preventive use.</p>\n<h3><br></h3>\n<h3><strong>Job Duties &amp; Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in planning, coordinating, and executing marketing campaigns and promotional activities.</li>\n  <li>Support social media management, including content creation, scheduling, and performance tracking across platforms such as Instagram, TikTok, Facebook, and LinkedIn.</li>\n  <li>Conduct market research and competitor analysis to identify industry trends, opportunities, and consumer insights.</li>\n  <li>Contribute to content creation, including blog articles, marketing copy, graphics, and digital assets.</li>\n  <li>Assist in organizing and supporting events, roadshows, product launches, and other marketing initiatives.</li>\n  <li>Provide general administrative and operational support for ongoing marketing projects.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Marketing, Communications, Business, or a related discipline.</li>\n  <li>Detail-oriented, responsible, and able to manage tasks efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Proactive, willing to learn, and comfortable taking initiative.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently as well as collaboratively within a dynamic, fast-paced team environment.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with major social media platforms (Instagram, TikTok, Facebook, LinkedIn).</li>\n  <li>Basic proficiency in design or editing tools (e.g., Premiere Pro, Photoshop, Illustrator, Canva, Adobe Creative Suite).</li>\n  <li>Able to commit for a duration of at least 3 to 6 months.</li>\n</ul>",
